{"type":"text","timestamp":1775841164374,"sessionID":"ses_2879f4fa6ffeNeJu6cDGH2BmtD","part":{"id":"prt_d7861a9b2001a3wOeLrWRH4GdJ","messageID":"msg_d7861940b001h3gcPvvYV0AXl6","sessionID":"ses_2879f4fa6ffeNeJu6cDGH2BmtD","type":"text","text":"Based on my verification, I found a discrepancy. The spec AR-003 requires a full client-go library at `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go`, but only the CRD types exist in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`.\n\n## Verification Results\n\n### What exists (pkg/apis):\n\n| Spec Requirement | Status |\n|------------------|--------|\n| `AgentRuntime` type | ✅ Matches |\n| `CodeInterpreter` type | ✅ Matches |\n| `AgentRuntimeList` / `CodeInterpreterList` | ✅ Matches |\n| `SchemeGroupVersion` (`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`) | ✅ Matches |\n| Constants (DefaultMaxSessionDuration, DefaultSessionTimeout, etc.) | ✅ Matches |\n| Tests | ✅ All 27 tests passing |\n\n### What's missing (client-go):\n\n| Component | Status |\n|-----------|--------|\n| Clientset with Interface | ❌ Not implemented |\n| RuntimeV1alpha1Client | ❌ Not implemented |\n| AgentRuntimeInterface / CodeInterpreterInterface | ❌ Not implemented |\n| Listers | ❌ Not implemented |\n| Informers | ❌ Not implemented |\n| Fake clients | ❌ Not implemented |\n\nThe spec references source at `/tmp/agentcube-ref/client-go/` which doesn't exist. The implementation only covers the CRD shared types and constants (the `pkg/apis` module), not the generated Kubernetes client library.\n\nShould I generate the client-go library or is this partial implementation intentional?","time":{"start":1775841164373,"end":1775841164373}}}
